Template Selection
As a user, I want to select a website template, so that I can start customizing my website.

Acceptance Criteria:
User can view a list of available templates.
User can select a template to start customization.
Tasks:
Design Template Selection Page (Frontend)

Subtask: Create a grid layout to display available templates.
Subtask: Add a preview feature for each template.
Implement Template Selection Logic (Backend)

Subtask: Create an API to fetch available templates.
Subtask: Store user-selected template in the database.
Test Template Selection Functionality

Subtask: Write test cases to ensure templates are displayed correctly.
Subtask: Validate that the selected template is stored properly.
